{
  "spec": {
    "title": "User Timing",
    "url": "https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/"
  },
  "algorithms": [
    {
      "html": "Stores a timestamp with the associated name (a \"mark\"). It MUST run these steps:",
      "rationale": "run",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "Run the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#dom-performancemark-constructor\" id=\"ref-for-dom-performancemark-constructor\">PerformanceMark constructor</a> and let <var>entry</var> be the newly created object."
        },
        {
          "html": "<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/performance-timeline/#dfn-queue-a-performanceentry\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-queue-a-performanceentry\">Queue a PerformanceEntry</a> <var>entry</var>."
        },
        {
          "html": "<a class=\"self-link\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#stored_mark\"></a>Add <var>entry</var> to the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/performance-timeline/#dfn-performance-entry-buffer\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-performance-entry-buffer\">performance entry buffer</a>."
        },
        {
          "html": "Return <var>entry</var>."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "html": "Removes the stored timestamp with the associated name. It MUST run these steps:",
      "rationale": "if",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "If <var>markName</var> is omitted, remove all <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#performancemark-performancemark\" id=\"ref-for-performancemark-performancemark①\">PerformanceMark</a> objects from the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/performance-timeline/#dfn-performance-entry-buffer\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-performance-entry-buffer①\">performance entry buffer</a>."
        },
        {
          "html": "Otherwise, remove all <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#performancemark-performancemark\" id=\"ref-for-performancemark-performancemark②\">PerformanceMark</a> objects listed in the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/performance-timeline/#dfn-performance-entry-buffer\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-performance-entry-buffer②\">performance entry buffer</a> whose <var>name</var> <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#string-is\" id=\"ref-for-string-is\">is</a> <var>markName</var>."
        },
        {
          "html": "Return <strong>undefined</strong>."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "html": "Stores the <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/hr-time/#typedefdef-domhighrestimestamp\" id=\"ref-for-typedefdef-domhighrestimestamp⑤\">DOMHighResTimeStamp</a></code> duration between two marks along with the associated name (a \"measure\"). It MUST run these steps:",
      "rationale": "if",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "If <var>startOrMeasureOptions</var> is a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#performancemeasureoptions-performancemeasureoptions\" id=\"ref-for-performancemeasureoptions-performancemeasureoptions\">PerformanceMeasureOptions</a> object and at least one of <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#performancemeasureoptions-start\" id=\"ref-for-performancemeasureoptions-start\">start</a>, <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#performancemeasureoptions-end\" id=\"ref-for-performancemeasureoptions-end\">end</a>, <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#performancemeasureoptions-duration\" id=\"ref-for-performancemeasureoptions-duration\">duration</a>, and <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#performancemeasureoptions-detail\" id=\"ref-for-performancemeasureoptions-detail\">detail</a> <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#map-exists\" id=\"ref-for-map-exists\">exist</a>, run the following checks:",
          "rationale": "if",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "If <var>endMark</var> is given, <a href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#dfn-throw\">throw</a> a <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#exceptiondef-typeerror\" id=\"ref-for-exceptiondef-typeerror\">TypeError</a></code>."
            },
            {
              "html": "If <var>startOrMeasureOptions</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#performancemeasureoptions-start\" id=\"ref-for-performancemeasureoptions-start①\">start</a> and <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#performancemeasureoptions-end\" id=\"ref-for-performancemeasureoptions-end①\">end</a> members are both omitted, <a href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#dfn-throw\">throw</a> a <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#exceptiondef-typeerror\" id=\"ref-for-exceptiondef-typeerror①\">TypeError</a></code>."
            },
            {
              "html": "If <var>startOrMeasureOptions</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#performancemeasureoptions-start\" id=\"ref-for-performancemeasureoptions-start②\">start</a>, <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#performancemeasureoptions-duration\" id=\"ref-for-performancemeasureoptions-duration①\">duration</a>, and <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#performancemeasureoptions-end\" id=\"ref-for-performancemeasureoptions-end②\">end</a> members all <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#map-exists\" id=\"ref-for-map-exists①\">exist</a>, <a href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#dfn-throw\">throw</a> a <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#exceptiondef-typeerror\" id=\"ref-for-exceptiondef-typeerror②\">TypeError</a></code>."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "html": "Compute <var>end time</var> as follows:",
          "rationale": "if",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "If <var>endMark</var> is given, let <var>end time</var> be the value returned by running the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#convert-a-mark-to-a-timestamp\" id=\"ref-for-convert-a-mark-to-a-timestamp\">convert a mark to a timestamp</a> algorithm passing in <var>endMark</var>."
            },
            {
              "html": "Otherwise, if <var>startOrMeasureOptions</var> is a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#performancemeasureoptions-performancemeasureoptions\" id=\"ref-for-performancemeasureoptions-performancemeasureoptions①\">PerformanceMeasureOptions</a> object, and if its <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#performancemeasureoptions-end\" id=\"ref-for-performancemeasureoptions-end③\">end</a> member <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#map-exists\" id=\"ref-for-map-exists②\">exists</a>, let <var>end time</var> be the value returned by running the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#convert-a-mark-to-a-timestamp\" id=\"ref-for-convert-a-mark-to-a-timestamp①\">convert a mark to a timestamp</a> algorithm passing in <var>startOrMeasureOptions</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#performancemeasureoptions-end\" id=\"ref-for-performancemeasureoptions-end④\">end</a>."
            },
            {
              "html": "Otherwise, if <var>startOrMeasureOptions</var> is a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#performancemeasureoptions-performancemeasureoptions\" id=\"ref-for-performancemeasureoptions-performancemeasureoptions②\">PerformanceMeasureOptions</a> object, and if its <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#performancemeasureoptions-start\" id=\"ref-for-performancemeasureoptions-start③\">start</a> and <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#performancemeasureoptions-duration\" id=\"ref-for-performancemeasureoptions-duration②\">duration</a> members both <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#map-exists\" id=\"ref-for-map-exists③\">exist</a>:",
              "rationale": "let",
              "steps": [
                {
                  "html": "Let <var>start</var> be the value returned by running the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#convert-a-mark-to-a-timestamp\" id=\"ref-for-convert-a-mark-to-a-timestamp②\">convert a mark to a timestamp</a> algorithm passing in <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#performancemeasureoptions-start\" id=\"ref-for-performancemeasureoptions-start④\">start</a>."
                },
                {
                  "html": "Let <var>duration</var> be the value returned by running the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#convert-a-mark-to-a-timestamp\" id=\"ref-for-convert-a-mark-to-a-timestamp③\">convert a mark to a timestamp</a> algorithm passing in <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#performancemeasureoptions-duration\" id=\"ref-for-performancemeasureoptions-duration③\">duration</a>."
                },
                {
                  "html": "Let <var>end time</var> be <var>start</var> plus <var>duration</var>."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "html": "Otherwise, let <var>end time</var> be the value that would be returned by the <code>Performance</code> object’s <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/hr-time-2/#dom-performance-now\"><code>now()</code></a> method."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "html": "Compute <var>start time</var> as follows:",
          "rationale": "if",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "If <var>startOrMeasureOptions</var> is a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#performancemeasureoptions-performancemeasureoptions\" id=\"ref-for-performancemeasureoptions-performancemeasureoptions③\">PerformanceMeasureOptions</a> object, and if its <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#performancemeasureoptions-start\" id=\"ref-for-performancemeasureoptions-start⑤\">start</a> member <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#map-exists\" id=\"ref-for-map-exists④\">exists</a>, let <var>start time</var> be the value returned by running the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#convert-a-mark-to-a-timestamp\" id=\"ref-for-convert-a-mark-to-a-timestamp④\">convert a mark to a timestamp</a> algorithm passing in <var>startOrMeasureOptions</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#performancemeasureoptions-start\" id=\"ref-for-performancemeasureoptions-start⑥\">start</a>."
            },
            {
              "html": "Otherwise, if <var>startOrMeasureOptions</var> is a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#performancemeasureoptions-performancemeasureoptions\" id=\"ref-for-performancemeasureoptions-performancemeasureoptions④\">PerformanceMeasureOptions</a> object, and if its <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#performancemeasureoptions-duration\" id=\"ref-for-performancemeasureoptions-duration④\">duration</a> and <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#performancemeasureoptions-end\" id=\"ref-for-performancemeasureoptions-end⑤\">end</a> members both <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#map-exists\" id=\"ref-for-map-exists⑤\">exist</a>:",
              "rationale": "let",
              "steps": [
                {
                  "html": "Let <var>duration</var> be the value returned by running the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#convert-a-mark-to-a-timestamp\" id=\"ref-for-convert-a-mark-to-a-timestamp⑤\">convert a mark to a timestamp</a> algorithm passing in <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#performancemeasureoptions-duration\" id=\"ref-for-performancemeasureoptions-duration⑤\">duration</a>."
                },
                {
                  "html": "Let <var>end</var> be the value returned by running the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#convert-a-mark-to-a-timestamp\" id=\"ref-for-convert-a-mark-to-a-timestamp⑥\">convert a mark to a timestamp</a> algorithm passing in <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#performancemeasureoptions-end\" id=\"ref-for-performancemeasureoptions-end⑥\">end</a>."
                },
                {
                  "html": "Let <var>start time</var> be <var>end</var> minus <var>duration</var>."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "html": "Otherwise, if <var>startOrMeasureOptions</var> is a <code>DOMString</code>, let <var>start time</var> be the value returned by running the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#convert-a-mark-to-a-timestamp\" id=\"ref-for-convert-a-mark-to-a-timestamp⑦\">convert a mark to a timestamp</a> algorithm passing in <var>startOrMeasureOptions</var>."
            },
            {
              "html": "Otherwise, let <var>start time</var> be <code>0</code>."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "html": "Create a new <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#performancemeasure-performancemeasure\" id=\"ref-for-performancemeasure-performancemeasure①\">PerformanceMeasure</a> object (<var>entry</var>) with <a href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this\">this</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#concept-relevant-realm\" id=\"ref-for-concept-relevant-realm\">relevant realm</a>."
        },
        {
          "html": "Set <var>entry</var>’s <code>name</code> attribute to <var>measureName</var>."
        },
        {
          "html": "Set <var>entry</var>’s <code>entryType</code> attribute to <code>DOMString \"measure\"</code>."
        },
        {
          "html": "Set <var>entry</var>’s <code>startTime</code> attribute to <var>start time</var>."
        },
        {
          "html": "Set <var>entry</var>’s <code>duration</code> attribute to the duration from <var>start time</var> to <var>end time</var>. The resulting duration value MAY be negative."
        },
        {
          "html": "Set <var>entry</var>’s <code>detail</code> attribute as follows:",
          "rationale": "if",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "If <var>startOrMeasureOptions</var> is a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#performancemeasureoptions-performancemeasureoptions\" id=\"ref-for-performancemeasureoptions-performancemeasureoptions⑤\">PerformanceMeasureOptions</a> object and <var>startOrMeasureOptions</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#performancemeasureoptions-detail\" id=\"ref-for-performancemeasureoptions-detail①\">detail</a> member <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#map-exists\" id=\"ref-for-map-exists⑥\">exists</a>:",
              "rationale": "let",
              "steps": [
                {
                  "html": "Let <var>record</var> be the result of calling the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/infrastructure.html#structuredserialize\" id=\"ref-for-structuredserialize\">StructuredSerialize</a> algorithm on <var>startOrMeasureOptions</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#performancemeasureoptions-detail\" id=\"ref-for-performancemeasureoptions-detail②\">detail</a>."
                },
                {
                  "html": "Set <var>entry</var>’s <a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#dom-performancemeasure-detail\" id=\"ref-for-dom-performancemeasure-detail\">detail</a> to the result of calling the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/infrastructure.html#structureddeserialize\" id=\"ref-for-structureddeserialize\">StructuredDeserialize</a> algorithm on <var>record</var> and the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#concept-current-everything\" id=\"ref-for-concept-current-everything\">current realm</a>."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "html": "Otherwise, set it to <code>null</code>."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "html": "<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/performance-timeline/#dfn-queue-a-performanceentry\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-queue-a-performanceentry①\">Queue a PerformanceEntry</a> <var>entry</var>."
        },
        {
          "html": "<a class=\"self-link\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#stored_measure\"></a>Add <var>entry</var> to the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/performance-timeline/#dfn-performance-entry-buffer\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-performance-entry-buffer③\">performance entry buffer</a>."
        },
        {
          "html": "Return <var>entry</var>."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "html": "Removes stored timestamp with the associated name. It MUST run these steps:",
      "rationale": "if",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "If <var>measureName</var> is omitted, remove all <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#performancemeasure-performancemeasure\" id=\"ref-for-performancemeasure-performancemeasure②\">PerformanceMeasure</a> objects in the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/performance-timeline/#dfn-performance-entry-buffer\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-performance-entry-buffer④\">performance entry buffer</a>."
        },
        {
          "html": "Otherwise remove all <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#performancemeasure-performancemeasure\" id=\"ref-for-performancemeasure-performancemeasure③\">PerformanceMeasure</a> objects listed in the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/performance-timeline/#dfn-performance-entry-buffer\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-performance-entry-buffer⑤\">performance entry buffer</a> whose <code>name</code> <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#string-is\" id=\"ref-for-string-is①\">is</a> <var>measureName</var>."
        },
        {
          "html": "Return <strong>undefined</strong>."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "html": "The <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#dom-performancemark-constructor\" id=\"ref-for-dom-performancemark-constructor①\">PerformanceMark constructor</a> must run the following steps:",
      "rationale": "if",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "If the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#current-global-object\" id=\"ref-for-current-global-object\">current global object</a> is a <code>Window</code> object and <var>markName</var> uses the same name as a <a href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#dfn-read-only\">read only attribute</a> in the <code><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/navigation-timing/#performancetiming-performancetiming\" id=\"ref-for-performancetiming-performancetiming\">PerformanceTiming</a></code> interface, <a href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#dfn-throw\">throw</a> a <a href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#syntaxerror\"><code>SyntaxError</code></a>."
        },
        {
          "html": "Create a new <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#performancemark-performancemark\" id=\"ref-for-performancemark-performancemark⑦\">PerformanceMark</a> object (<var>entry</var>) with the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#current-global-object\" id=\"ref-for-current-global-object①\">current global object</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#concept-global-object-realm\" id=\"ref-for-concept-global-object-realm\">realm</a>."
        },
        {
          "html": "Set <var>entry</var>’s <code>name</code> attribute to <var>markName</var>."
        },
        {
          "html": "Set <var>entry</var>’s <code>entryType</code> attribute to <code>DOMString \"mark\"</code>."
        },
        {
          "html": "Set <var>entry</var>’s <code>startTime</code> attribute as follows:",
          "rationale": "if",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "If <var>markOptions</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#performancemarkoptions-starttime\" id=\"ref-for-performancemarkoptions-starttime\">startTime</a> member <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#map-exists\" id=\"ref-for-map-exists⑦\">exists</a>, then:",
              "rationale": "if",
              "steps": [
                {
                  "html": "If <var>markOptions</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#performancemarkoptions-starttime\" id=\"ref-for-performancemarkoptions-starttime①\">startTime</a> is negative, throw a <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#exceptiondef-typeerror\" id=\"ref-for-exceptiondef-typeerror③\">TypeError</a></code>."
                },
                {
                  "html": "Otherwise, set <var>entry</var>’s <code>startTime</code> to the value of <var>markOptions</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#performancemarkoptions-starttime\" id=\"ref-for-performancemarkoptions-starttime②\">startTime</a>."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "html": "Otherwise, set it to the value that would be returned by the <code>Performance</code> object’s <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/hr-time-2/#dom-performance-now\"><code>now()</code></a> method."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "html": "Set <var>entry</var>’s <code>duration</code> attribute to <code>0</code>."
        },
        {
          "html": "If <var>markOptions</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#performancemarkoptions-detail\" id=\"ref-for-performancemarkoptions-detail\">detail</a> is null, set <var>entry</var>’s <a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#dom-performancemark-detail\" id=\"ref-for-dom-performancemark-detail\">detail</a> to null."
        },
        {
          "html": "Otherwise:",
          "rationale": "let",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "Let <var>record</var> be the result of calling the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/infrastructure.html#structuredserialize\" id=\"ref-for-structuredserialize①\">StructuredSerialize</a> algorithm on <var>markOptions</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#performancemarkoptions-detail\" id=\"ref-for-performancemarkoptions-detail①\">detail</a>."
            },
            {
              "html": "Set <var>entry</var>’s <a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#dom-performancemark-detail\" id=\"ref-for-dom-performancemark-detail①\">detail</a> to the result of calling the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/infrastructure.html#structureddeserialize\" id=\"ref-for-structureddeserialize①\">StructuredDeserialize</a> algorithm on <var>record</var> and the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#concept-current-everything\" id=\"ref-for-concept-current-everything①\">current realm</a>."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "convert a mark to a timestamp",
      "href": "https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#convert-a-mark-to-a-timestamp",
      "html": "To <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-export=\"\" id=\"convert-a-mark-to-a-timestamp\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">convert a mark to a timestamp</dfn>, given a <var>mark</var> that is a <code>DOMString</code> or <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/hr-time/#typedefdef-domhighrestimestamp\" id=\"ref-for-typedefdef-domhighrestimestamp①⓪\">DOMHighResTimeStamp</a></code> run these steps:",
      "rationale": "if",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "If <var>mark</var> is a <code>DOMString</code> and it has the same name as a <a href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#dfn-read-only\">read only attribute</a> in the <code><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/navigation-timing/#performancetiming-performancetiming\" id=\"ref-for-performancetiming-performancetiming①\">PerformanceTiming</a></code> interface, let <var>end time</var> be the value returned by running the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#convert-a-name-to-a-timestamp\" id=\"ref-for-convert-a-name-to-a-timestamp\">convert a name to a timestamp</a> algorithm with <var>name</var> set to the value of <var>mark</var>."
        },
        {
          "html": "Otherwise, if <var>mark</var> is a <code>DOMString</code>, let <var>end time</var> be the value of the <code>startTime</code> attribute from the most recent occurrence of a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#performancemark-performancemark\" id=\"ref-for-performancemark-performancemark⑧\">PerformanceMark</a> object in the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/performance-timeline/#dfn-performance-entry-buffer\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-performance-entry-buffer⑥\">performance entry buffer</a> whose <code>name</code> <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#string-is\" id=\"ref-for-string-is②\">is</a> <var>mark</var>. If no matching entry is found, <a href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#dfn-throw\">throw</a> a <a href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#syntaxerror\"><code>SyntaxError</code></a>."
        },
        {
          "html": "Otherwise, if <var>mark</var> is a <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/hr-time/#typedefdef-domhighrestimestamp\" id=\"ref-for-typedefdef-domhighrestimestamp①①\">DOMHighResTimeStamp</a></code>:",
          "rationale": "if",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "If <var>mark</var> is negative, throw a <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#exceptiondef-typeerror\" id=\"ref-for-exceptiondef-typeerror④\">TypeError</a></code>."
            },
            {
              "html": "Otherwise, let <var>end time</var> be <var>mark</var>."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "convert a name to a timestamp",
      "href": "https://w3c.github.io/user-timing/#convert-a-name-to-a-timestamp",
      "html": "To <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"convert-a-name-to-a-timestamp\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">convert a name to a timestamp</dfn> given a <var>name</var> that is a <a href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#dfn-read-only\">read only attribute</a> in the <code><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/navigation-timing/#performancetiming-performancetiming\" id=\"ref-for-performancetiming-performancetiming②\">PerformanceTiming</a></code> interface, run these steps:",
      "rationale": "if",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "If the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#global-object\" id=\"ref-for-global-object\">global object</a> is not a <code>Window</code> object, <a href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#dfn-throw\">throw</a> a <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#exceptiondef-typeerror\" id=\"ref-for-exceptiondef-typeerror⑤\">TypeError</a></code>."
        },
        {
          "html": "If <var>name</var> is <code>navigationStart</code>, return <code>0</code>."
        },
        {
          "html": "Let <var>startTime</var> be the value of <code>navigationStart</code> in the <code><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/navigation-timing/#performancetiming-performancetiming\" id=\"ref-for-performancetiming-performancetiming③\">PerformanceTiming</a></code> interface."
        },
        {
          "html": "Let <var>endTime</var> be the value of <var>name</var> in the <code><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/navigation-timing/#performancetiming-performancetiming\" id=\"ref-for-performancetiming-performancetiming④\">PerformanceTiming</a></code> interface."
        },
        {
          "html": "If <var>endTime</var> is <code>0</code>, <a href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#dfn-throw\">throw</a> an <a href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#invalidaccesserror\"><code>InvalidAccessError</code></a>."
        },
        {
          "html": "Return result of subtracting <var>startTime</var> from <var>endTime</var>."
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}